    <item>
      <title>伊隆·马斯克计划在宾夕法尼亚战场为特朗普竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/elon-musk-to-campaign-for-donald-trump-in-pennsylvania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，埃隆·马斯克计划本月在宾夕法尼亚州为唐纳德·特朗普竞选，该州可能决定总统大选的最终胜出者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/elon-musk-to-campaign-for-donald-trump-in-pennsylvania</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 20:16:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和哈里斯利用播客争取选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/trump-harris-embrace-podcasts-in-2024-election-for-tuned-out-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯全力投入播客，提供约会建议、个人理财技巧和深入流行文化的节目正在吸引对这两位总统候选人的采访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/trump-harris-embrace-podcasts-in-2024-election-for-tuned-out-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 20:02:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯的税收计划因竞选承诺遭遇现实而受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/reeves-s-tax-plans-falter-as-election-pledges-meet-reality</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当英国首相凯尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 和财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 策划工党在英国的执政之路时，他们希望通过提高私募股权和超级富豪“非本地”居民的税收来为关键支出计划提供资金。现在，这些承诺正在变成现实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/reeves-s-tax-plans-falter-as-election-pledges-meet-reality</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:12:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列与哈马斯开战一周年，多条战线同时作战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-says-it-intercepted-hamas-rockets-as-war-marks-one-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防军称，他们拦截了哈马斯和其他伊朗支持的组织向特拉维夫发射的大部分火箭弹。经过一年的战争，双方周一在多个战线上的战斗进一步升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-says-it-intercepted-hamas-rockets-as-war-marks-one-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 15:56:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯导弹击中第二艘粮食船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/ukraine-says-russia-missile-hit-ship-loaded-with-corn-for-export</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据基辅基础设施部称，俄罗斯周一向一艘满载乌克兰谷物的船只发射了一枚弹道导弹，这是两天内第二起此类事件，造成一人死亡，五人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/ukraine-says-russia-missile-hit-ship-loaded-with-corn-for-export</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯和特朗普纪念哈马斯袭击以色列一周年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/harris-trump-mark-oct-7-milestone-with-mideast-still-aflame</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一年前的 10 月 7 日，哈马斯武装分子攻入以色列南部，此后，其引发的动乱和不确定性继续影响着整个中东地区 — — 以及白宫的激烈角逐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/harris-trump-mark-oct-7-milestone-with-mideast-still-aflame</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
